TITLE: Running Pipe Widget Process
DESCRIPTION: Executes a Pipe Widget process using the `yao run` command.  The Widget ID is specified in the command. Arguments can be passed to the process.  If interrupted by user input, a context ID is returned for resuming execution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/yaoapp/yao/blob/main/pipe/README.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
yao run pipes.<Widget.ID> [args...]
```

